Results of the GEE analysis for the primary outcomes of depression symptoms (MADRS) are summarised in Table 2. Considering all post-baseline time points during the trial treatment phase, there were no significant differential changes in levels of depression symptoms between rosuvastatin and placebo (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
